{{Otheruses|Mynock}}
'''Mynock Puffing''' was a game which was engaged in by several sport hunters. It involved attaching [[Helium/Legends|helium]]-based grenades to a [[Mynock/Legends|mynock]], and, due to their allergic reaction to helium, they would swell up and explode.

